WEBVTT

00:00.461 --> 00:02.733
Previously on Scream Queens...

00:03.080 --> 00:05.875
Looks like we're gonna need to
call a Green Meanie summit.

00:05.953 --> 00:08.709
We are here to review the
past and future kills.

00:10.093 --> 00:13.228
Chanel Oberlin <i>fried
my sister's face off.</i>

00:13.296 --> 00:15.831
Help me!

00:15.899 --> 00:17.833
I'm Chanel #3, Cassidy's girlfriend.

00:17.901 --> 00:19.968
She is going to have to die.

00:20.036 --> 00:21.904
<i>We can put Denise in the freezer</i>

00:21.971 --> 00:23.806
until they find a cure
for being electrocuted.

00:25.642 --> 00:27.846
<i>You, Dr. Brock
Holt,</i> are a killer.

00:28.268 --> 00:31.880
<i>I have a disease called Kuru.</i> It
is terminal. I'll be dead in a month.

00:31.948 --> 00:33.582
You guys are gonna kill me, aren't you?

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
